	</div><h1 class="blog_entrytitle">
		Case Of the Lucrative Lure - Part XI
	</h1>
<div class="blogs_entryattribution">
		<a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20100707131141/http://it.toolbox.com/people/chiefmonkey/" class="hoverS">Security Monkey</a>&nbsp;<span class="blogs_postdetails">(Information Security Investigator / CISO)&nbsp;posted&nbsp;5/16/2006 | <a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20100707131141/http://it.toolbox.com/blogs/securitymonkey/case-of-the-lucrative-lure-part-xi-9334#commentsform" class="hoverS">Comments</a>&nbsp;(5)</span>
